final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Since there is a cyan KeyDoor at (18, 8) which blocks the path to the goal, the agent must pick up the yellow Key at (13, 8) first. Align the agent on the horizontal axis (x=13) by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Then, move DOWN to reach the key (y=8). Next, pick up the Key by moving into its space. Now, while holding the Key, move RIGHT to reach the cyan KeyDoor at (18, 8) and open it. Finally, move to reach the goal (x=19, y=11) by moving DOWN 11 - 8 = 3 times and then RIGHT 1 time.
